About Me
Hello, my name is Srihith Garlapati and I am from Fremd High School.
About the Project
My project, Cars and Their Mileage will be comparing the weights of cars with their mileage.
Goals
see which is the best car to buy weight wise and mileage wise
see which is the worst car to buy weight wise and mileage wise
but it will be hard to show this goal
